snippet.textDisplay: At 0:59 Forge says "don't worry" but he isn't saying it to her, he is saying it to us. Pause it when he says it, he is looking directly into the camera? Also, he touches his medal, at the same time there seems to be two very distinctly different sounds. One sound, the more prominent, is the clanking of metal (presumably Revenant's hand changing to his sword-thing) the other almost sounds like an engine shutting down, or some for of electrical equipment turning off anyway. Could that mean something? Or am I reading to far into this? Also, everyone is talking about Revenant killing Forge, no one seems to be questioning why he killed him though. To what end? Is it personal? Was it just to get a foot hold in the game? Or was it something to do with Hammond Robotics? Possibly revenge? A message sent? "Stay away from the Apex Games."? What was his reason for killing Forge? Was Forge even real? Or was he a "forged" character to through peoples gaze away from Revenant? "Some still believe that you are not ready to be an Apex Legend" is that Respawn telling us that Forge isn't ready? That he is still under development? What do you people think?

Could that mean something? Or am I reading to far into this? Also, everyone is talking about Revenant killing Forge, no one seems to be questioning *why* he killed him though. To what end? snippet.textDisplay:
Alright, so my theory Forge is still alive, There was a youtuber said the Forge that was killed was not the real Forge, why? The Forge on the picture has green eyes and no scars, but in the interview the Forge has brown eyes and scars, that means he is not the real Forge, so is Forge still alive? In my opinion yes he is, and who's the new Legend in S4? Revenant or Forge? Some people may think Revenant is the new legend, i agreed but what about Forge? I think he's still gonna be the new legend, so in S4 we have 2 new legends? Maybe, and why Revenant killed Forge? In my opinion he killed Forge because he wanted to be the new legend in apex, but i'm not sure i'm still waiting for the new trailer

Thank you if yo reading till now.
And do you think i should make a content about a theory?
